.\" ###### Setup ############################################################
.Dd May 22, 2026
.Dt gs\-resize\-with\-cropping 1
.Os gs\-resize\-with\-cropping
.\" ###### Name #############################################################
.Sh NAME
.Nm gs\-resize\-with\-cropping
.Nd resizes an image, including cropping to fit a changed aspect ratio.
.\" ###### Synopsis #########################################################
.\" Manpage syntax help:
.\" https://forums.freebsd.org/threads/howto-create-a-manpage-from-scratch.13200/
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Ar input\_filename Ar output\_filename
.br
.Op Fl A Ar aspect\_ratio | Fl Fl aspect Ar aspect\_ratio
.br
.Op Fl A Ar H:V|HxV | Fl Fl aspect Ar H:V|HxV
.br
.Op Fl A Ar A0|...|A9|An | Fl Fl aspect Ar A0|...|A9|An
.br
.Op Fl A Ar keep | Fl Fl aspect Ar keep
.br
.Op Fl W Ar new\_width | Fl Fl width Ar new\_width
.br
.Op Fl H Ar new\_height | Fl Fl height Ar new\_height
.br
.Op Fl q | Fl Fl quiet
.Op Fl w | Fl Fl verbose
.Nm gs\-resize\-with\-cropping
.Op Fl h | Fl Fl help
.Nm gs\-resize\-with\-cropping
.Op Fl v | Fl Fl version
.\" ###### Description ######################################################
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm gs\-resize\-with\-cropping
resizes an image, including cropping to fit a changed aspect ratio.
.Pp
.\" ###### Arguments ########################################################
.Sh ARGUMENTS
The following options are available:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Ar input\_filename
The input image. Any format supported by GraphicsMagick can be used. The format will be detected automatically.
.It Ar output\_filename
The name for the output image to be written. Any format supported by GraphicsMagick can be used. The format will be detected by the provided file name extension (e.g. .jpeg, .png, .webp, .pdf, ...). An existing output file will be overwritten.
.It Fl A Ar aspect\_ratio | Fl Fl aspect Ar aspect\_ratio
Specifies the aspect ratio directly as value (e.g. 1.414214).
.It Fl A Ar H:V|HxV | Fl Fl aspect Ar H:V|HxV
Specifies the aspect ratio as H:V or HxV (e.g. 16:9 or 16x9).
.It Fl A Ar A0|...|A9|An | Fl Fl aspect Ar A0|...|A9|An
Specifies the aspect ratio as DIN An format ratio (A1, A2, ..., A9, or An; i.e. sqrt(2):1 ≈ 1.414213562373).
.It Fl A Ar keep | Fl Fl aspect Ar keep
Leaves the aspect ratio unchanged. This is the default.
.It Fl W Ar new\_width | Fl Fl width Ar new\_width
Specifies the new width. Then, the new height is calculated based on the configured aspect ratio.
.It Fl H Ar new\_height | Fl Fl height Ar new\_height
Specifies the new height. Then, the new width is calculated based on the configured aspect ratio.
.It Fl q | Fl Fl quiet
Quiet mode: suppress status output. This is the default.
.It Fl w | Fl Fl verbose
Verbose mode: print status output and processing details.
.It Fl h | Fl Fl help
Prints the program's command\-line parameters and exits.
.It Fl v | Fl Fl version
Prints the program version and exits.
.El
.\" ###### Exit status ######################################################
.Sh EXIT STATUS
The
.Nm
tool exits with 0 on success, and >0 in case of an error.
.\" ###### Examples #########################################################
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Bergen.jpeg Bergen\-1920\-4:3.webp \-\-aspect 4:3 \-\-width 1920 \-\-verbose
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Bergen.jpeg Bergen\-1920\-16:9.png \-A 16x9 \-W 1920
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Bergen.jpeg Bergen\-3860\-A3.pdf \-\-aspect A3 \-\-width 3840
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Bergen.jpeg Bergen\-1024\-An.jpeg \-A 1.414214 \-W 1024
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping Portobello.jpeg Portobello\-2048\-16:9.jpeg \-A 16:9 \-\-width 2048 \-v
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping \-\-help
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping \-h
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping \-\-version
.It gs\-resize\-with\-cropping \-v
.El
